<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-3346] Rename &quot;Mode&quot; to &quot;SslMode&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3346</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the channel builders, the Mode enum is undocumented, so it is unclear that it is used to signify whether the connection is for SSL client or SSL server.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suggest renaming to SslMode (although adding documentation will be ok too, if people object to the rename)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12947819">KAFKA-3346</key>
